*********************************
*****
*****  C / C++ PROGRAMMING  *****
*****
*********************************

The C and C++ Programming Languages are at the heart of all computer programming
languages in general. Most compiler "backends" have been written in C/C++, and
they include Perl, Python, Ruby, D, and Go.

For those using Linux, there is a script named "setup-cpp-linux.sh" which will
download various C, and C++ programming language related documentation to your
computer. It will require Subversion (SVN), Git and Hg (Mercurial) to be
installed.


